reviewText: My 7 year old (boy) purchased this with a gift card he got for his birthday and he LOVED all four of these movies.  Never even minded that the actors weren't all the same in each film.  He just loved the scooby doo movies.  If you kid is a fan, this will be a good purchase.

Great find. Have a 3 year old yhat loves Scooby doo and he loves these movies.  5 stars

First 2 movies have some A-list actors/actresses and are extremely enjoyable. After that the next movies were straight to DVD and the acting is shaky at best, but the kids still enjoy them and that's who we bought them for after all. So I say great value and you can't go wrong with this purchase.
